<%= @subject %>

<% @holds.each do |hold| %>
- <%= hold.item.name %> (<%= hold.item.complete_number %>) is now available!
<% end %>

Please login to your account and schedule an appointment to pick your items up:

<%= new_account_appointment_url %>

<% if @holds.any? { |hold| hold.item.hold_duration.present? } %>
* Some of your items have a short hold window to help keep them circulating. Please schedule your pickup as soon as possible so you don't miss out!
<% else %>
* If you aren't able to get an item in the next 7 days, it will become available for another member.
<% end %>

* If you no longer wish to borrow an item, please cancel the hold in your account so it can be borrowed by another member.
